}.md5sum ls 01.rawdata/*/*.fq.gz | parallel -j 5 --progress --dryrun md5sum {} &#39;&gt;&#39; tmp/{/}.md5sum ls 01.rawdata/*/*.fq.gz | parallel -j 5 --progress md5sum {} &#39;&gt;&#39; tmp/{/}.md5sum Note: &quot;&gt;&quot; should be quoted to prevent from being interpreted as redirection by shell. GNU parallel: --dryrun don't actually run command -j 5 run 5 jobs in parallel --progress show progress -I STRING set replacement string, default is '{}' {} place holder for input sources {/} removes the path {.} removes the extension {/.} removes path and extension {//} keeps only the path {#} gives the job number {number} individual input columns could be specified with {1}, {2.}, {3//}, {4/.} et al. 另一种调用parallel的方法是使用here-document，示例如下:
